mixin collaboration(params)
	+nav-panel.nav-panel--fixed
	.bg-gray-1.pt-5.mt-4
		.container.py-4.py-md-5
			h1.h2.text-conax-blue.text-uppercase.font-700.mb-3.mb-md-4 Discover Networking
			p.p-l.mb-md-5 Networking structures your target space from your interests, requests, posts, and other activities. Customizes collected content into Creative Networks and integrates with ConAx Tool to collaborative work.
			.hero-card.align-items-center.flex-sm-row-reverse.my-4.mb-md-n5
				.hero-card_text.hero-card_item.px-md-5.py-3
					p.p-l Compile your content through flexible algorithm of decentralized platform.  Maximum personalization of content in accordance with current requests and strategic interests.
				.hero-card_image.hero-card_item.hero-card_image--stretch
					img(src="images/collaboration-picture.jpg").mx-auto.d-block
			.hero-card.align-items-center.my-4.my-md-n5
				.hero-card_text.hero-card_item.px-md-5.py-3
					p.p-l Integrates and aggregates your content and activities with Open Call, Call to Action and Get in functions and converse your access to ConAx Tool.
						a(href="#").text-curious-blue See more ConAx Tool
				.hero-card_image.hero-card_item.hero-card_image--stretch
					img(src="images/collaboration-picture-02.jpg").mx-auto.d-block
			.hero-card.align-items-center.flex-sm-row-reverse.my-4.mt-md-n5
				.hero-card_text.hero-card_item.px-md-5.py-3
					p.p-l It integrates your content and activity with the ConAx tool, and makes it easier to manage your activites and communication in the environment.
				.hero-card_image.hero-card_item.hero-card_image--stretch
					img(src="images/collaboration-picture-03.jpg").mx-auto.d-block
			p.p-l.mt-md-5.my-4.px-md-5.text-center It integrates your content and activity with the ConAx tool, and makes it easier to manage your activites and communication in the environment.
			img(src="images/collaboration-picture-04.jpg").w-md-auto.w-100.mx-auto.d-block.mb-3
	+footer
	+social#social-float.social-float.social-vertical.hide
	+scrollToTop#scroll-to-top.hide